 47 Author·······National·Instruments
 48 ===========··=================================================================================================================================
  
 49 About
 50 =====
  
 51 The·**nidaqmx**·package·contains·an·API·(Application·Programming·Interface)
 52 for·interacting·with·the·NI-DAQmx·driver.·The·package·is·implemented·in·Python.
 53 The·package·is·implemented·as·a·complex,·
 54 highly·object-oriented·wrapper·around·the·NI-DAQmx·C·API·using·the·
 55 `ctypes·<https://docs.python.org/2/library/ctypes.html>`_·Python·library.
  
 56 **nidaqmx**·supports·all·versions·of·the·NI-DAQmx·driver·that·ships·with·the·C
 57 API.·The·C·API·is·included·in·any·version·of·the·driver·that·supports·it.·The
 58 **nidaqmx**·package·does·not·require·installation·of·the·C·header·files.
  
 59 Some·functions·in·the·**nidaqmx**·package·may·be·unavailable·with·earlier·
 60 versions·of·the·NI-DAQmx·driver.·Visit·the·
 61 `ni.com/downloads·<http://www.ni.com/downloads/>`_·to·upgrade·your·version·of·
 62 NI-DAQmx.
  
 63 **nidaqmx**·supports·Windows·and·Linux·operating·systems·where·the·NI-DAQmx
 64 driver·is·supported.·Refer·to
 65 `NI·Hardware·and·Operating·System·Compatibility·<https://www.ni.com/r/hw-support>`_
 66 for·which·versions·of·the·driver·support·your·hardware·on·a·given·operating
 67 system.
  
 68 **nidaqmx**·supports·CPython·3.7+·and·PyPy3.
  
 69 Installation
 70 ============
  
 71 Running·**nidaqmx**·requires·NI-DAQmx·to·be·installed.·Visit
 72 `ni.com/downloads·<http://www.ni.com/downloads/>`_·to·download·the·latest
 73 version·of·NI-DAQmx.·None·of·the·recommended·**Additional·items**·are·required
 74 for·**nidaqmx**·to·function,·and·they·can·be·removed·to·minimize·installation
 75 size.·It·is·recommended·you·continue·to·install·the·**NI·Certificates**·package
 76 to·allow·your·Operating·System·to·trust·NI·built·binaries,·improving·your
 77 software·and·hardware·installation·experience.
  
 78 **nidaqmx**·can·be·installed·with·`pip·<http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip>`_::
  
 79 ··$·python·-m·pip·install·nidaqmx
